<div class="w-4/5">
  <h1>ValidationForm</h1>
  <p>This component houses FormField components and collects their validations during form submission.</p>
  <p>Field results are keyed by their field's <code>name</code> property and is merged into the forms resulting hash.</p>
  <p>When the form submits, the <code>onSubmit</code> action is invoked yielding a hash of promises that hold the validation results of its fields.</p>
  {{outlet}}
</div>

